        {
            "id": 6312206,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 摩根士丹利(MS-US)大漲5.04%，報189.89美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>摩根士丹利(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MS-US</a>)截至台北時間15日23:21股價上漲9.11美元，報189.89美元，漲幅5.04%，成交量3,100,843（股），盤中最高價189.89美元、最低價181.00美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.6%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.55%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.73%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+3.31%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>摩根士丹利(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MS-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-1.1%</li> <li>近 1 月：+2.8%</li> <li>近 3 月：+17.65%</li> <li>近 6 月：+26.94%</li> <li>今年以來：+0.47%</li></ul></section></main>",
